1. Developer Information
Spring app 

2. Steps to delete an account
Outlined below are the systematic procedures for the deletion of a user account and the comprehensive removal of all associated data:

1. On the home screen, please select the three-line menu icon located at the top right corner of the screen:

2. Upon accessing the options menu, kindly proceed by selecting 'Settings' from the available choices:
        


3. Select the 'Remove Me from Study' button. A confirmation prompt will then appear, requesting verification for account deletion. Please confirm by clicking 'Yes' on this prompt.




3. Data Deletion and retention:
Upon completion of the deletion process, we ensure that no data will be retained. The following categories of data will be comprehensively removed from our records: user data, all completed questionnaires, and any derived insights

